USER APPLICATION ACTIVATE PAYMENT GATEWAY API IN YOUR WIFI IP ADDRESS:
1. Open the user applictaion code folder in android studio.
2. Open RetrofitInstance kotlin file in the kotlin folder. (The only orange kotlin file icon in the folder)
3. Search your wifi ip address using your terminal / Command Prompt, then type "ifconfig" to get your ip address.
4. Copy your ip address then replace your ip address with "192.168.0.249" in .baseUrl("http://192.168.0.249/stripe-android-api/").
5. Run the app.